Best place to find your bright future
Dev Bhoomi Uttarakhand University

Dehradun, the cultural & educational centre of Uttarakhand, is home to a cutting-edge campus of the best university of Dehradun Uttarakhand. The University has developed into one of India's top academic institutions since its founding in 2005. At that time it was recognised as Dev Bhoomi Institute of Technology(DBIT) and after 17 years of excellent journey it is now rebranded as Dev Bhoomi Uttarakhand University.

DBUU as the Best University in Dehradun is a perfect example of how cultural diversity and heritage can coexist with modernity from the twenty-first century. The University consists of 15,000+ alumni and 10 Schools that offers a wide range of undergraduate, diploma, and postgraduate programmes in a variety of disciplines like engineering, computer applications, architecture, design (B.Des), management, commerce, hotel management, mass communication, BAMS, fashion design, agriculture, polytechnic, horticulture, microbiology, nursing, and pharmacy. Offering a range of over 120 uniquely structured programs, designed to suit the career prospects of every student aspirant.
The 42-acre lush green campus is home to over 20,000 students from 29 States, making Dev Bhoomi Uttarakhand University a culturally global destination. Every student is uniquely shaped by our multidisciplinary network of knowledgeable faculty, corporate partnerships, collaborative research, and fellowship programmes to shape the world.
